{"tid":1563521,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"盛世美顏被網狂飆6字髒話！37歲女星韓藝瑟「粗話回應」超霸氣","createTime":"2019-09-12T12:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T13:45:44.000Z","uid":9573,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8ba6a5efb9f61a1ca62e7912b304062fe401e294","tid":1563521,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:16:21.000Z","msg":"南韓37歲女星韓藝瑟，擁有超乎常人的驚艷美貌，還有性感9頭身比例的傲人曲線，再加上自然不做作的個性，是不少人心目中的女神，去年發生醫療糾紛後，她成功回到演藝圈，還常會透過社群平台與粉絲交流，沒想到日前她上傳自拍照的貼文底下，竟然被網友寫下髒話，對此她也以還不虛偽的用髒話回應，再度顯現霸氣女王的氣勢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/09/12/2126416-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F09%2F12%2F2126416-XXL.jpg&h=d93e5729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲韓藝瑟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/09/12/2126408-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F09%2F12%2F2126408-XXL.jpg&h=ed995db2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓藝瑟日前在梳化完成之後，拿起手機對著鏡子拍下了2張自拍照，對成果相當滿意的她，立刻上傳到IG上與網友分享，可見照片中她頂著中分長直髮，穿上大U字白色短版上衣，搭配白紅色高腰褲，露出纖細又迷人的小蠻腰，其中她的唇膏特別用2種顏色做混合，立刻吸引了大眾的目光，不少網友頻頻稱讚，「哇！真的是女神」、「太美麗了」、「為何美到看不見歲月的痕跡」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/09/12/2126409-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F09%2F12%2F2126409-XXL.jpg&h=763c11dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲韓藝瑟曝光驚為天人的美照。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/09/12/2126411-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F09%2F12%2F2126411-XXL.jpg&h=ada6bea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，有一名網友在留言處寫了超多的髒話，只見網友寫下「這不是要罵人，這是我所能使用的詞彙中最大值，真是他X的太美了，XX是人嗎？是畫嗎？，還會有配備 58kWh 和 77kWh 的延長續航力版本，是藝術嗎？是女神嗎？什麼啊！他X的太美了」，結果就被其他網友注意到這則留言，累積至今已有520個人按讚，就連韓藝瑟本人都回應這名網友，還和對方一樣寫下髒話，「他X的太感謝了」，意外引起網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/09/12/2126413-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F09%2F12%2F2126413-XXL.jpg&h=419d2039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲韓藝瑟和粉絲用「髒話」交流。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/09/12/2126432-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F09%2F12%2F2126432-XXL.jpg&h=ba64d91d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dff31faf608bf9256662726fbcaa495ead6a7e9","tid":1563521,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:17:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"06a2a68019af234f79e89ed730198a9dd1e61f08","tid":1563521,"uid":63505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:19:49.000Z","msg":"當年茶煲呀四係好正又感人"},{"pid":"5f27947f321292382d42013327388c3391db4d34","tid":1563521,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:38:32.000Z","msg":"聽都未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d648702ec1e0dc4ec282d405fba9a217bc2871fb","tid":1563521,"uid":200280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"rep